<subSubSection id="CCFD0CC3FFFB014763A5F4F391308D68" pageId="25" pageNumber="48" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="84585F48FFFB014763A5F4F391308D68" blockId="25.[151,760,1267,1610]" pageId="25" pageNumber="48">
<emphasis id="B693835AFFFB014763A5F4F392688E28" bold="true" box="[151,281,1267,1290]" pageId="25" pageNumber="48">Comments.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="43E724CBFFFB01476212F4F391718E28" authorityName="Jacoby" authorityYear="1894" box="[288,512,1267,1290]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Platyxantha" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="48" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="dohertyi">
<emphasis id="B693835AFFFB01476212F4F391718E28" box="[288,512,1267,1290]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="48">Platyxantha dohertyi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was classified in different genera by various authors. 
<bibRefCitation id="E07622B9FFFB014762D2F513910E8E08" author="WILCOX J. A." box="[480,639,1299,1322]" editor="WILCOX J. A." firstAuthor="WILCOX" journalOrPublisher="Editio seconda. W. Junk, ' s-Gravenhage" pageId="25" pageNumber="48" pagination="433 - 664" refId="ref33616" refString="WILCOX J. A. 1973: Chrysomelidae: Galerucinae: Luperini: Luperina. In: WILCOX J. A. (ed.): Coleopterorum Catalogus Supplementa. Pars 78 (3). Editio seconda. W. Junk, ' s-Gravenhage, pp. 433 - 664." title="Chrysomelidae: Galerucinae: Luperini: Luperina" type="book chapter" volumeTitle="Coleopterorum Catalogus Supplementa. Pars 78 (3)." year="1973">WILCOX (1973)</bibRefCitation>
catalogued it in 
<taxonomicName id="43E724CBFFFB014763E2F533914F8E68" authority=", MOHAMEDSAID (1998 a)" authorityName=", MOHAMEDSAID" authorityYear="1998" box="[208,574,1331,1354]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Polexima" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="48" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B693835AFFFB014763E2F53392478E68" box="[208,310,1331,1354]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="48">Polexima</emphasis>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="E07622B9FFFB0147627AF533914F8E68" author="MOHAMEDSAID M. S." box="[328,574,1331,1354]" firstAuthor="MOHAMEDSAID" journalOrPublisher="Serangga" pageId="25" pageNumber="48" pagination="67 - 85" part="3" refId="ref32759" refString="MOHAMEDSAID M. S. 1998 a: Checklist of the Galerucinae from Taman Negara Gunung Gading, Sarawak (Coleoptera: Chrysomelidae). Serangga 3: 67 - 85." title="Checklist of the Galerucinae from Taman Negara Gunung Gading, Sarawak (Coleoptera: Chrysomelidae)" type="journal article" year="1998" yearSuffix="a">MOHAMEDSAID (1998a)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
transferred it to 
<taxonomicName id="43E724CBFFFB014763A5F55392498E48" authorityName="Laboissiere" authorityYear="1933" box="[151,312,1363,1386]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Hoplosaenidea" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="48" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B693835AFFFB014763A5F55392498E48" box="[151,312,1363,1386]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="48">Hoplosaenidea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
based on examination of a 
<typeStatus id="5B5CE1EAFFFB01476153F55391C58E48" box="[609,692,1363,1386]" pageId="25" pageNumber="48">syntype</typeStatus>
in the MCZ, and finally 
<bibRefCitation id="E07622B9FFFB0147626DF57391358EA8" author="MOHAMEDSAID M. S." bookContentInfo="239 pp." box="[351,580,1395,1418]" firstAuthor="MOHAMEDSAID" journalOrPublisher="Pensoft, Sofia-Moscow" pageId="25" pageNumber="48" refId="ref32942" refString="MOHAMEDSAID M. S. 2004: Catalogue of the Malaysian Chrysomelidae (Insecta: Coleoptera). Pensoft, Sofia-Moscow, 239 pp." title="Catalogue of the Malaysian Chrysomelidae (Insecta: Coleoptera)" type="book" year="2004">MOHAMEDSAID (2004)</bibRefCitation>
transferred it to 
<taxonomicName id="43E724CBFFFB014763A5F593927C8E88" authorityName="Thunberg" authorityYear="1814" box="[151,269,1427,1450]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Taumacera" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="48" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B693835AFFFB014763A5F593927C8E88" box="[151,269,1427,1450]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="48">Taumacera</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
without any explanation. Based on the study of a female 
<typeStatus id="5B5CE1EAFFFB014763C6F5B392378EE8" box="[244,326,1459,1482]" pageId="25" pageNumber="48">syntype</typeStatus>
deposited in the BMNH and a photograph of the male 
<typeStatus id="5B5CE1EAFFFB0147622FF5D392018EC8" box="[285,368,1491,1514]" pageId="25" pageNumber="48">syntype</typeStatus>
from the MCZ, I fully concur with 
<bibRefCitation id="E07622B9FFFB014763A5F5F392068D28" author="MOHAMEDSAID M. S." bookContentInfo="239 pp." box="[151,375,1523,1546]" firstAuthor="MOHAMEDSAID" journalOrPublisher="Pensoft, Sofia-Moscow" pageId="25" pageNumber="48" refId="ref32942" refString="MOHAMEDSAID M. S. 2004: Catalogue of the Malaysian Chrysomelidae (Insecta: Coleoptera). Pensoft, Sofia-Moscow, 239 pp." title="Catalogue of the Malaysian Chrysomelidae (Insecta: Coleoptera)" type="book" year="2004">MOHAMEDSAID (2004)</bibRefCitation>
that 
<taxonomicName id="43E724CBFFFB0147629BF5F391F78D28" authorityName="Jacoby" authorityYear="1894" box="[425,646,1523,1546]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Platyxantha" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="48" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="dohertyi">
<emphasis id="B693835AFFFB0147629BF5F391F78D28" box="[425,646,1523,1546]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="48">Platyxantha dohertyi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
belongs to 
<taxonomicName id="43E724CBFFFB014763A5F61392468D08" authorityName="Laboissiere" authorityYear="1933" box="[151,311,1555,1578]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Hoplosaenidea" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="48" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B693835AFFFB014763A5F61392468D08" box="[151,311,1555,1578]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="48">Hoplosaenidea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. The reason why Mohamedsaid transferred it later to 
<taxonomicName id="43E724CBFFFB014763CCF63392048D68" authorityName="Thunberg" authorityYear="1814" box="[254,373,1587,1610]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Taumacera" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="48" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B693835AFFFB014763CCF63392048D68" box="[254,373,1587,1610]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="48">Taumacera</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is unknown to me.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
